          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped carrot</strong>, <strong>onion</strong> and<strong> garlic</strong> and cook for 6-8 or until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
